http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/Teacher-held-on-charge-of-misbehaving-with-student/article13998585.ece

The Chikkamagaluru Town police on Wednesday arrested a school teacher on the charge of misbehaving with one of his students.The police gave the name of the accused as Shankarappa. The accised, allegedly touched the private parts of a 13-year-old student in the school on Wednesday.The student brought the incident to the notice of her parents, who, later filed a complaint with the police.The Chikkamagaluru Town police arrested the school teacher on the charge of misbehaving with a girl student.The police registered a case against the accused under the relevant sections of the Protection of Children from Sexual Offences Act 2012.